		<fdd:adoption>AVI is widely adopted for video production and filemaking; commentator <a href="http://www.jmcgowan.com/avicodecs.html">John McGowan</a> writes, "Most PC video capture and editing systems capture video to AVI files using Motion JPEG video compression."</fdd:adoption>
